metadata.description:
Inspired By is an exclusive Music + Art NFT Series, curating incredible visual NFT artists and pairing them with amazing musicians to create special 1/1s inspired by the music.
Vol. 1 features Platinum Recording Artist JEM premiering her song ‘RAINBOW’, with accompanying artworks by Varvara Alay, Aslan Ruby, Gabe Weis and Rik Lee. 15 signed editions of each artwork, 60 editions in total.
10% of primary sales goes to charity.
